name: ModuleMetadataStatus

text.div:
ModuleMetadataStatus

The status of the knowledge module

This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/module-metadata-status defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
draft DraftThe module is in draft state
active ActiveThe module is active
inactive InactiveThe module is inactive, either rejected before publication, or retired after publication
